The paper discusses computer-assisted reading and analysis of text, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of OLAP for quick analysis of multidimensional data suggests a focus on data management and analysis, which could fall under databases (cs.DB) or cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the mention of humanities and social sciences suggests a potential focus on digital humanities (cs.DL).
